21:58.000Z","msg":"好多年前食完鏞記<br />\n有個侍應呀叔同我地吹水<br />\n問我地啲野食點<br />\n我地話隻燒鵝唔好食<br />\n最離譜係凍嘅<br />\n佢話輔左廚師之後都有好多人投訴過<br />\n但佢地都冇辦法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a32e0cb8d88c3f07eec4cd10c5c8084bbc252f0","tid":922204,"uid":196099,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"87ff52745b578162a49c422c1f15e309258aaf2c","tid":922204,"uid":145769,"like":5,"dislike":72,"score":-67,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"落單前都明碼實價，唔覺佢厄人<br />\n佢燒䳘係好食架喎<br />\n<br />\n反而炒飯唔值咁貴<br />\n唔差，但細碟，要百尾二百"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:25:35.000Z","msg":"佢啲鵝好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n上次去食凍架，叫佢先肯換過碟<br />\n甘牌都算係唔錯<br />\n以前三聖食海鮮嘅啲燒鵝都ok<br />\n但係而家，真係大部分都垃圾黎"},{"pid":"1a26042f20a46f6a1236a083408be997c3424649","tid":922204,"uid":693,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"quote":{"pid":"87ff52745b578162a49c422c1f15e309258aaf2c","tid":922204,"uid":145769,"like":5,"dislike":72,"score":-67,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:01:50.000Z","msg":"落單前都明碼實價，唔覺佢厄人<br />\n佢燒䳘係好食架喎<br />\n<br />\n反而炒飯唔值咁貴<br />\n唔差，但細碟，要百尾二百"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"䳘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f66131edf1581e3f1f739cf3a3d81a3d768d2726","tid":922204,"uid":51532,"like":6,"dislike":12,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:40:49.000Z","msg":"豆苗幾錢斤落街市睇下啦屌你老母，真係幾能好笑，價錢就寫能晒起個水牌到，食完先話貴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06d671e5e3deca3bf72a7db39c0c2cb9026d0596","tid":922204,"uid":98386,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-30T08:55:26.000Z